=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Evan Thomas","active":false,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"To test this, I started with the stack below\r\n{code}\r\n{\r\n  \"AWSTemplateFormatVersion\":\"2010-09-09\",\r\n  \"Resources\":{\r\n    \"Group1\":{\r\n      \"Type\":\"AWS::IAM::Group\",\r\n      \"Properties\":{\r\n        \"Path\":\"/myapplication/\",\r\n        \"Policies\":[\r\n          {\r\n            \"PolicyName\":\"myapppolicy0\",\r\n            \"PolicyDocument\":{\r\n              \"Version\":\"2012-10-17\",\r\n              \"Statement\":[\r\n                {\r\n                  \"Effect\":\"Allow\",\r\n                  \"Action\":[\r\n                    \"ec2:*\"\r\n                  ],\r\n                  \"Resource\":[\r\n                    \"*\"\r\n                  ]\r\n                },\r\n                {\r\n                  \"Effect\":\"Deny\",\r\n                  \"Action\":[\r\n                    \"s3:*\"\r\n                  ],\r\n                  \"NotResource\":[\r\n                    \"*\"\r\n                  ]\r\n                }\r\n              ]\r\n            }\r\n          },\r\n          {\r\n            \"PolicyName\":\"myapppolicy1\",\r\n            \"PolicyDocument\":{\r\n              \"Version\":\"2012-10-18\",\r\n              \"Statement\":[\r\n                {\r\n                  \"Effect\":\"Allow\",\r\n                  \"Action\":[\r\n                    \"cloudwatch:*\"\r\n                  ],\r\n                  \"Resource\":[\r\n                    \"*\"\r\n                  ]\r\n                },\r\n                {\r\n                  \"Effect\":\"Deny\",\r\n                  \"Action\":[\r\n                    \"sqs:*\"\r\n                  ],\r\n                  \"NotResource\":[\r\n                    \"*\"\r\n                  ]\r\n                }\r\n              ]\r\n            }\r\n          },\r\n          {\r\n            \"PolicyName\":\"myapppolicy2\",\r\n            \"PolicyDocument\":{\r\n              \"Version\":\"2012-10-19\",\r\n              \"Statement\":[\r\n                {\r\n                  \"Effect\":\"Allow\",\r\n                  \"Action\":[\r\n                    \"autoscaling:*\"\r\n                  ],\r\n                  \"Resource\":[\r\n                    \"*\"\r\n                  ]\r\n                },\r\n                {\r\n                  \"Effect\":\"Deny\",\r\n                  \"Action\":[\r\n                    \"sns:*\"\r\n                  ],\r\n                  \"NotResource\":[\r\n                    \"*\"\r\n                  ]\r\n                }\r\n              ]\r\n            }\r\n          }\r\n        ]\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  },\r\n  \"Outputs\":{\r\n    \"Group1Ref\":{\r\n      \"Value\":{\r\n        \"Ref\":\"Group1\"\r\n      }\r\n    },\r\n    \"Group1Arn\":{\r\n      \"Value\":{\r\n        \"Fn::GetAtt\":[\r\n          \"Group1\",\r\n          \"Arn\"\r\n        ]\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n{code}\r\nThen I did the following things\r\n1) Create the stack, try removing one of the policies then deleting stack (works)\r\n2) Create the stack, try adding a policy then deleting the stack (does not work, and should not work)\r\n3) Create the stack, delete the group, then delete the stack (works)\r\n4) Create the stack, modify the template to add a new policy, remove another policy.  (Works)\r\n5) Create the stack, modify the template to add a new policy, remove another policy, change path.  (Works).\r\n\r\n","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=ethomas","name":"ethomas","key":"ethomas","accountId":"557058:8f092f9a-0724-44c0-84a3-0220705f856a","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/a01d066493c57e5dee4b94dc87395576?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FavatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3D